lines.text: You out there! Come one step closer and Old Bess will spit in your eye.
Hi, Kate! Take it easy, it's...
That'll teach you to talk back to a lady! And the next time you come pesterin' around here, remember Annie Oakley and I went to the same finishin' school.
[while hiding behind a haystack, Rex starts to yodel]
Well, sufferin' sassafras. All right, you ornery nightingale, come out - and don't miss that D-flat or I'll blow your head off!
